org.apache.beam.it.gcp.dataflow

Class AbstractPipelineLauncher

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.beam.it.gcp.dataflow.AbstractPipelineLauncher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.beam.it.common.PipelineLauncher
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClassicTemplateClient, DefaultPipelineLauncher, FlexTemplateClient

    public abstract class AbstractPipelineLauncher
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.apache.beam.it.common.PipelineLauncher
    Abstract class covering the common operations between Classic and Flex templates.

    Generally, the methods here are the ones that focus more on the Dataflow jobs rather than launching a specific type of template.
